descriptionHtml:
This ENB is my customized ENB. There are four options(on two different sections) for this file.

1. DOF Styles-Strong/Weak
2. Saturation-High Sat/Low Sat

What this ENB Does!
1. It adds DOF effect(through ENB)
2. It will modify colors and feelings of the game. I kind of exaggerated Red in order to give a vampire-like feeling : D(However, Low Saturation version does not)

-Notes-
No SSAO!
No Bloom!
High FPS!







That\'s about it : D

Mono ENB Reference
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15069

For d3d9.dll file: go to
http://enbdev.com/index_en.html
then go to [Download], Click Tesv, And download the v0.113. NOT 114!
